### Steps to reproduce the behaviour

When I drag and drop a group to an "Automatic * Group" destination, the moved group is no longer displayed in the tree.

This happens because the group becomes the child of an "Automatic Group", which does not allow having children outside the collection criteria

This bug also happens in the shared database, but drag and drop is a changement that is not synchronized, and therefore less dangerous.

